{
  "stem": "19921.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 187.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I knew how to read the Torah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that was-- you know, that was education.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The education itself was very thorough education.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I went to public school, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as far as graduation, I remember I graduated in 1937.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was nice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was nice.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had sports and everything else, and I participated in sport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was very good in sports.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I participated in every sport there and was placed on the first team-- my school team.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Mostly soccer, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no-- and volleyball.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was a big thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And hockey during the winter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as I say, I-- it was-- it was-- it was good.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I did not feel any antisemitism myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Maybe if you would have asked my father or, or my grandfather, they would probably have different opinions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I, as a child, did not felt that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So that's-- I have good memories.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was not-- no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no fighting over religion at all in my school, in my class.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had no, no such thing like fighting over religion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never was called, you know-- yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They would mention, you know, like [POLISH], which meant Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, something was said, but not in any derogatory manner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because we marched together in ev-- whenever there was a, you know, national holiday, or something like that, everybody dressed up the same way, and everyone marched.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But, of course, we had in our class-- as I remember, we had in our class Hasidic children with payots.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were not bothered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were not bothered in class.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But don't forget, my town was a very modern town.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
